[
	{
		"id": 0,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "ボス！　荷物全部積みました！\nおやつも３００コール以内です！ なんとぴったり！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00670",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 1,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "遠足にでも行くつもりか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00671",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 2,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "う……ごめんなさい、ふざけました",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00672",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 3,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "……そういえば来ませんね。アルビーナさんたち",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00673",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 4,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "何やら騒動が起こっているようだったからな。\nとはいえ……噂をすれば、だぞ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00674",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 5,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "あ、エルスさん！　それにタイニー！\n１週間ぶり！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00675",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 6,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "アルビーナさん！！　しばらく見かけなかったから\n山のように心配したんですよ～！！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00676",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 7,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "先日言っていた「決着」とやらは付いたのか？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00677",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 8,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "付いたとも言えないんですけど……とりあえず\n先送りにはできた、かな？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00678",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 9,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "あらら、ちゃんと解決はしてないんですかね？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00679",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 10,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "まあ、それはそれとして！　前話した通り、\nベスティラ行き、アタシたちも同行希望です！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00680",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 11,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "そのことですけど、本当にいいんですか？\n今行くのは、正直おすすめしないですけど……",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00681",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 12,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "その心は？",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_036_00682",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 13,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "少々訳ありでな。しかもその訳が悪化していそうだ。\n何かしらの騒動に巻き込まれる危険もある",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00683",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 14,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "何かあったとき、ボスは私を守るので\nアルビーナさんたちを守れないかもしれません～",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00684",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 15,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "……市民の安全が第一。何を守られる気でいるんだ。\nお前もアルビーナたちを守るんだ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00685",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 16,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "は、はいっ！　もちろんです！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00686",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 17,
		"localized_name": "ベップ",
		"romanized_name": "Bepp",
		"model_path_hash": "3101416597918110218",
		"text": "その点は大丈夫。姉様は私が守るから",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_151_036_00687",
		"still_path_hash": "5045460652135134961",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 18,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "頼りにしてるよ～ベップぅ～。\nそれにこっちも、神聖国の使命があるわけだしね",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00688",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 19,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "「九偉人図」の捜索が神聖国の使命というのは\n気になるがな",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00689",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 20,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "そこはあまり聞かないでもらえると助かるっす！\n歴史的価値がある分、神聖国として集めてるってことで",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00690",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 21,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "色々迷惑をかけてしまうかもしれないので……\nすんません",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00691",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 22,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "神聖国の案内人の言葉がそれなら、深入りはしないが",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00692",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 23,
		"localized_name": "エルス",
		"romanized_name": "Els",
		"model_path_hash": "5033911810886101706",
		"text": "……話せる時が来たら話してくれ。心配だからな。\nこれは監察官としてではなく、友人としての言葉だ",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_222_036_00693",
		"still_path_hash": "532943395044460292",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 24,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "……りょーかいっす！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00694",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 25,
		"localized_name": "タイニー",
		"romanized_name": "Tiny",
		"model_path_hash": "2428915022803462192",
		"text": "さて、それでは行きますよ～。\n皆さんのことは、私たちが守りますので！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_221_036_00695",
		"still_path_hash": "5609327809530807165",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 26,
		"localized_name": "アルビーナ",
		"romanized_name": "Alvina",
		"model_path_hash": "2668606804942549205",
		"text": "一島民として監察局のお力\n当てにさせていただきやす！",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_150_036_00696",
		"still_path_hash": "8874763601186801212",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	},
	{
		"id": 27,
		"localized_name": "ジョゼ",
		"romanized_name": "José",
		"model_path_hash": "0",
		"text": "ベスティラ……か",
		"voice_file": "VOICE_MAIN_223_036_00697",
		"still_path_hash": "1488533364831425921",
		"speech_balloon_type_id": 780292254
	}
]